| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4634 — Recovery Inhibition (interlock)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 507338ef-9cd8-5653-bf39-d14da76fcff9"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
